&lt;/h6>&lt;h2 id="段落">段落
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Markdown is a lightweight and easy-to-use markup language that allows you to write formatted text using a plain-text editor.
It is widely used for creating documentation, writing articles, and creating content for websites and blogs.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Markdown syntax is simple and intuitive, making it easy to learn and use. It supports various formatting options such as
headings, bold and italic text, lists, links, images, and more. With just a few keystrokes, you can create well-structured
and visually appealing content.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="引用">引用
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>引用的内容会显示为灰色背景，使用&lt;code>&amp;gt;&lt;/code>来表示引用。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="在引用中使用markdown语法">在引用中使用markdown语法
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;gt; Tiam, ad mint andaepu dandae nostion secatur sequo quae.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;gt; **Note** that you can use *Markdown syntax* within a blockquote.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>效果&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Tiam, ad mint andaepu dandae nostion secatur sequo quae.
&lt;strong>Note&lt;/strong> that you can use &lt;em>Markdown syntax&lt;/em> within a blockquote.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="引用中使用cite标记">引用中使用cite标记
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;gt; Don&amp;#39;t communicate by sharing memory, share memory by communicating.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&amp;gt; — &amp;lt;cite&amp;gt;Rob Pike[^1]&amp;lt;/cite&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[^1]: Rob Pike&amp;#39;s [talk](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PAAkCSZUG1c) during Gopherfest, November 18, 2015.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>效果&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Don&amp;rsquo;t communicate by sharing memory, share memory by communicating.&lt;br>
— &lt;cite>Rob Pike&lt;sup id="fnref:1">&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref">1&lt;/a>&lt;/sup>&lt;/cite>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="表格">表格
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>表格不是markdown的标准语法，但HUGO支持表格。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="在表格中使用markdown语法">在表格中使用markdown语法
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-mysql" data-lang="mysql">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Italics&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Bold&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Code&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">------&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1">-- | -------- | ------ |
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">italics&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">**&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bold&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">**&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">code&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">|&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>效果&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th>Italics&lt;/th>
&lt;th>Bold&lt;/th>
&lt;th>Code&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>&lt;em>italics&lt;/em>&lt;/td>
&lt;td>&lt;strong>bold&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
&lt;td>&lt;code>code&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;p>代码&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
